subTreeLevelToShow - This is number represents the nodes subtree-depth. 0 means, only the SocietyTypeNode should be shown, nothing more. 1 means, the SocietyTypeNode, and the SocietyInstanceNodes should be shown, because these are 1 level deeper; same with 3, 4, and so on.
